<div class="bs-header">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="col-md-5">
			<%= image_tag ("trebek.png") %>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-7">
			<h1>jService</h1>
			<h2>108,000+ Trivia Questions</h2>
			<p>A set of trivia services by <a href="http://github.com/sottenad">@sottenad</a></p>
			<p><a href="https://github.com/sottenad/jService" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">View On Github</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
	<div class="col-md-7">
		<h3>About</h3>
		<p>This is in large part a project to learn a bit about screen-scraping and creating an easily consumable set of services for public consumption. I will be offering this free of charge, but on a very small Heroku instance until sufficient demand exists. That said, please don't use this for production purposes without grabbing the project and hosting it elsewhere, as I cannot ensure performance.</p>
		<h3>Usage</h3>
		<p>jService exposes two endpoints, <code>/api/random</code> and <code>/api/clues</code>. Use random to pull a random clues from all 30 years, or use clues to filter your clues.</p>
		<h4>/Clues</h4>
		<ul>
			<li>Url: <code>/api/clues</code></li>
			<li>Options (POST or GET data):
				<ul>
					<li><code>value</code>(int): the value of the clue in dollars</li>
					<li><code>min_date</code>(date): earliest date to show, based on original air date</li>
					<li><code>max_date</code>(date): latest date to show, based on original air date</li>
					<li><code>offset</code>(int): offsets the displayed clues when returning more than 1	00</li>
				</ul>
		</ul> 
		<h4>/Random</h4>
		<ul>
			<li>Url: <code>/api/random</code></li>
			<li>Options (POST or GET data):
				<ul>
					<li><code>count</code>(int): amount of clues to return, limited to 100 at a time</li>
				</ul>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-5">
		<div class="panel panel-default" id="quiz-question">
			<div class="panel-heading">
				<h4>Random Question<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-refresh" id='refresh-question'></span></h4>
				
			</div>
			<div class="panel-body">

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>	
</div>

<script id="quiz-template" type="text/x-handlebars-template">
	<p>Difficulty: {{value}}</p>
	<h3>{{{category.title}}}</h3>
	<h4>{{{question}}}</h4>
	<p id="show-answer">{{{answer}}}</p>
</script>

